	(text "PCB heatsink dissipation\nDerating file give 3v3 max current: 0.155A\nwe will take 0.3A max for power calculation\nworst case: (5*1.05-3.235)*0.3 = 0.6W\nTamb: 50°C\nbased on AN044_EN.pdf figure 11:\nfor a Copper area of 100mm² the SOT can dissipate up to 0.7W with Ta 50°C\na cooper area of 100mm² around the thermal pad is mandatory\n"
